This was first intended to be Stored Procedure, but I was getting a lot of bugs related to the version I was coding in (Azure Data Studio (ADS) - 
Retiring IN 02.28.2026. This can be recreated in Visual Studio Code. 

The script was created to perform the ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) process to populate the 'silver' schema tables from the 'bronze' schema.

Actions Performed:

  - Truncates Silver tables.
  - Inserts transformed and cleanned data from Bronze into Silver tables.
  - Displays Duration Time per process and also for the entire batch after completion.

Usage Example:

Just Copy, Paste it and Run it.
